OL,6,F25 women have received compensation
OL,7,Ffrom Betsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,8,FBoard following gynaecological surgery
OL,9,Fcarried out by one surgeon.
OL,11,FOver recent months, S4C's current
OL,12,Faffairs programme Y Byd ar Bedwar has
OL,13,Fbeen investigating the work of
OL,14,Fgynaecological surgeon Derek Klazinga,
OL,15,Fwho was employed by the health board
OL,16,Fbetween 2002 and 2016.
