OL,4,Cboard after surgery by one doctor
OL,6,FMany of the women were compensated on
OL,7,Fthe grounds that Mr Klazinga failed to
OL,8,Fobtain fully informed consent before
OL,9,Fcarrying out surgery, and did not
OL,10,Fadequately explain the potential side
OL,11,Feffects and risks of treatment. One
OL,12,Fwoman has received compensation as
OL,13,Frecently as April 2025 - Kerry Watson
OL,14,Ffrom Kinmel Bay in north Wales.
OL,16,FKerry underwent surgery in 2014 after
OL,17,Fbeing diagnosed with bladder prolapse
OL,18,Fat the age of 29, a condition that can
OL,19,Fcause involuntary urine leakage.
