OL,6,F"I was leaking when I exerted myself
OL,7,For tried to play with the boys or pick
OL,8,Fthem up ` I've got three boys," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FDuring the operation, Mr Klazinga
OL,12,Fimplanted two types of artificial mesh
OL,13,Fto support Kerry's organs.
OL,15,F"When I woke up the next morning, I
OL,16,Fhad this awful pain in my back, on the
OL,17,Fleft side," she said. "The pain was
OL,18,Foff the scale. I've never felt
OL,19,Fanything like it."
