OL,7,Fimproved. She now takes around 120
OL,8,Ftablets a week, and in 2024 was
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with post-traumatic stress
OL,10,Fdisorder (PTSD).
OL,12,F"I didn't want to be here anymore. I
OL,13,Fcouldn't deal with the pain, I
OL,14,Fcouldn't deal with the thoughts I
OL,15,Fhad," she said. "I was nobody, just a
OL,16,Fbag of pain. Ten long years of that.
