OL,6,FIn 2023, Kerry came across a law
OL,7,Ffirm's website advertising cases
OL,8,Fagainst Betsi Cadwaladr University
OL,9,FHealth Board related to surgery
OL,10,Fcarried out by Derek Klazinga. She
OL,11,Fthen began her own legal case against
OL,12,Fthe health board, in which a
OL,13,Fgynaecology expert said she didn't
OL,14,Fneed this complex mesh surgery. That
OL,15,Fexpert claimed a simpler, less
OL,16,Fintrusive treatment, like injections
OL,17,For a pessary would've eased Kerry's
OL,18,Fsymptoms.
