OL,6,FBetsi Cadwaladr denied injections
OL,7,Fwould have been appropriate for Kerry,
OL,8,Fbut they admitted that other non-
OL,9,Fsurgical treatments, such as vaginal
OL,10,Fprolapse pessaries, should have been
OL,11,Fdiscussed with her and that the
OL,12,Fprocess of obtaining Kerry's consent
OL,13,Ffor the surgery fell below the
OL,14,Fstandard to be expected of a
OL,15,Freasonable, competent surgeon.
OL,17,F"I wasn't told about the risks
OL,18,Finvolved with TVT-O mesh. I didn't
OL,19,Freceive the correct information before
OL,20,Fthe surgery."
