OL,6,FIn April 2025, Kerry received
OL,7,Fcompensation from the health board on
OL,8,Fthe grounds that she was not offered
OL,9,Fan alternative treatment to TVT-O mesh
OL,10,Fsurgery and that she was not fully
OL,11,Finformed of the risks of having TVT-O
OL,12,Fmesh surgery.
OL,14,F"I was initially offered a low amount,
OL,15,Fso I declined their first offer," she
OL,16,Fsaid. "I ended up accepting #110,000
OL,17,Fand then fees are taken off that"
OL,19,FAfter paying legal fees, Kerry was
OL,20,Fleft with #97,200.
