OL,6,F"Is that going to cover all those
OL,7,Fnights I'll be up crying in pain? That
OL,8,Fdoesn't touch the sides, really."
OL,10,FY Byd ar Bedwar has spoken to seven
OL,11,Fwomen in north Wales who have received
OL,12,Fcompensation following surgery carried
OL,13,Fout by Mr Klazinga. Several say they
OL,14,Fdid not consent to the procedures they
OL,15,Funderwent, and most describe chronic
OL,16,Fpain that has had a devastating impact
OL,17,Fon their lives.
