OL,6,FSolicitor Michael Strain, from
OL,7,FPwllheli, has represented a client who
OL,8,Fbrought a case against the health
OL,9,Fboard after being treated by Mr
OL,10,FKlazinga.
OL,12,F"It's very unusual for one individual
OL,13,Fto have so many cases against them,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"This is a scandal. How can one person
OL,17,Fhave so many cases brought against
OL,18,Fthem without the board informing
OL,19,Fpatients that there are so many
OL,20,Fclaims? There needs to be far more
OL,21,Ftransparency about what has happened."
