OL,7,FKlazinga was due to appear before a
OL,8,FGeneral Medical Council fitness-to-
OL,9,Fpractise hearing in 2021, but removed
OL,10,Fhis name from the medical register
OL,11,Fbefore the scheduled date, which meant
OL,12,Fthat the hearing never took place.
OL,14,FIn a statement to Y Byd ar Bedwar,
OL,15,FDerek Klazinga said:
