OL,6,F"Firstly, I wish to express my
OL,7,Fsincerest sympathy that these ladies
OL,8,Fhave had to endure such physical and
OL,9,Fpsychological pain caused by, what we
OL,10,Fnow know to be, defective medical
OL,11,Fproducts used in their treatments."
OL,13,F"These products were identified as
OL,14,Fpotentially harmful and temporarily
OL,15,Fbanned in 2018. This was followed in
OL,16,F2020 by a National Enquiry: The
OL,17,FIndependent Medicines and Medical
OL,18,FDevices Safety Review, chaired by
OL,19,FBaroness Julia Cumberlege."
