OL,6,F"I ceased practising medicine 10 years
OL,7,Fago, more than two years before the
OL,8,Fban. Before retiring in 2016, I always
OL,9,Fpractised with the patient at the
OL,10,Fcentre of my care, while abiding by
OL,11,Fthe first principle of medicine:
OL,12,F'First, do no harm'. I acted with the
OL,13,Futmost professionalism and integrity.
OL,14,FI was, of course, completely unaware
OL,15,Fof the defective nature of the
OL,16,Fproducts, which wasn't subsequently
OL,17,Fexposed until two years after I
OL,18,Fretired."
