OL,6,FThe Y Byd ar Bedwar team gave Mr
OL,7,FKlazinga several opportunities to take
OL,8,Fpart in an interview and explained
OL,9,Fthat they are aware of the dangers of
OL,10,Fthe mesh itself but wanted an
OL,11,Fexplanation as to why he had failed to
OL,12,Fexplain the side effects and
OL,13,Fcomplications of the operations to the
OL,14,Fpatients and why he had not obtained
OL,15,Ftheir full consent. He did not respond
OL,16,Fto these points.
