OL,6,FThe use of TVT and TVT-O mesh has been
OL,7,Fsuspended in Wales since 2018
OL,8,Ffollowing patient safety concerns.
OL,9,FWhile we do not know which
OL,10,Fmanufacturer made the mesh used by
OL,11,FDerek Klazinga during the surgery of
OL,12,Fthe 25 women concerned, we do know
OL,13,Fthat some manufacturers have paid
OL,14,Fsettlements for complications arising
OL,15,Ffrom mesh surgery while not admitting
OL,16,Fliability.
OL,18,FDr Clara Day, Executive Medical
OL,19,FDirector at Betsi Cadwaladr University
OL,20,FHealth Board, said:
