OL,6,F"Firstly, I want to sincerely
OL,7,Fapologise to all women who have
OL,8,Fsuffered complications through the
OL,9,Finsertion of vaginal mesh after
OL,10,Ftreatment within our Health Board.
OL,11,FAcross the UK, we know a number of
OL,12,Fclaims have been settled and I want to
OL,13,Facknowledge the stress and pain this
OL,14,Fhas caused to a small proportion of
OL,15,Fwomen in our region who underwent
OL,16,Fthose procedures.
