OL,6,F"Since I became BCUHB's Executive
OL,7,FMedical Director in September last
OL,8,Fyear, I have been made aware of some
OL,9,Fhistoric claims in relation to one
OL,10,Fclinician who left the Health Board in
OL,11,F2016. Via the legal system, we have
OL,12,Facknowledged physical harm to some
OL,13,Fpatients who underwent procedures and
OL,14,Fwe have found record keeping and
OL,15,Fconsent had not been completed to the
OL,16,Frequired standard in a number of cases.
